    <h3 itemprop="headline">Planes carrying 19 Australians linked to the Islamic State group land in Melbourne and Sydney</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Two planes carrying 19 Australian women and children linked to the Islamic State group in Syria have landed in Melbourne and Sydney.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/05/26/19-australian-women-and-children-linked-to-islamic-state-group-set-to-return-from-syria/"  >(Rod Mcguirk, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
