    <h3 itemprop="headline">Mother, boyfriend allegedly abandoned blindfolded young sons in remote forest as part of 'game': reports</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Marine Rousseau and Marc Ballabriga allegedly abandoned her two young children in a forest in Europe, blindfolding them as part of a so-called game.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/05/26/mother-boyfriend-allegedly-abandoned-blindfolded-young-sons-remote-forest-part-game/"  >(Fox News)</a>
