    <h3 itemprop="headline">Iran signals &#8216;mass sacrifice&#8217; in 'high stakes' Saddam-era warning amid Trump deal talks</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Expert says Iran&apos;s Pezeshkian mapped a foundational wartime symbol onto current U.S. and Israel tensions, signaling Tehran won&apos;t back down easily.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/05/25/iran-signals-mass-sacrifice-high-stakes-saddam-era-warning-amid-trump-deal-talks/"  >(Fox News)</a>
