    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/world/2026/05/27/in-congo-displacement-camp-fighting-ebola-with-sand-oatmeal-and-one-thermometer-but-no-water.webp" alt="In Congo displacement camp, fighting Ebola with sand, oatmeal and one thermometer but no water" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">In Congo displacement camp, fighting Ebola with sand, oatmeal and one thermometer but no water</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      There is one handwashing station and one infrared thermometer to fight the Ebola epidemic in this camp for 10,000 displaced people in Bunia, a city at the heart of the outbreak in eastern Congo.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/05/27/in-congo-displacement-camp-fighting-ebola-with-sand-oatmeal-and-one-thermometer-but-no-water/"  >(Justin Kabumba And Monika Pronczuk, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
