    <h3 itemprop="headline">Muslim pilgrims converge on Mount Arafat in Saudi Arabia as the Hajj reaches its peak</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Muslim pilgrims have gathered on Mount Arafat in Saudi Arabia for the second day of the Hajj, considered the pinnacle of the annual pilgrimage.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/05/26/muslim-pilgrims-converge-on-mount-arafat-in-saudi-arabia-as-the-hajj-reaches-its-peak/"  >(Baraa Anwer And Mariam Fam, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
