  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/tech/2026/05/20/san-francisco-turns-to-ai-to-avoid-collisions-between-ships-and-whales-searching-for-food.webp" alt="San Francisco turns to AI to avoid collisions between ships and whales searching for food" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">San Francisco turns to AI to avoid collisions between ships and whales searching for food</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Climate change is pushing starving gray whales into the San Francisco Bay in unusual numbers, where ship strikes killed at least 40% of the 21 whales found dead last year.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/05/20/san-francisco-turns-to-ai-to-avoid-collisions-between-ships-and-whales-searching-for-food/"  >(Annika Hammerschlag, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
