    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">She has 400,000 Instagram followers and major brand deals. She&#8217;s also AI</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      At first glance, Aitana Lopez could be any other influencer. Her Instagram feed is a mix of Pilates workouts, model shoots, and photos posing in front of Coachella’s iconic Ferris wheel and inside the Alo gym.
The 27-year-old is a Scorpio.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/05/22/she-has-400000-instagram-followers-and-major-brand-deals-shes-also-ai/"  >(Eve Upton-Clark, Fast Company)</a>
