    <h3 itemprop="headline">This free email security scanner pairs perfectly with Gmail or Outlook</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Last summer, I stumbled onto a brilliantly useful tool that ended up being one of the most well-received discoveries we’ve ever shared in these quarters.
It was seemingly so popular, in fact, that its hobbyist nature couldn’t keep up with the demand.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/05/23/free-email-security-scan-gmail-outlook-snitcher-space/"  >(JR Raphael, Fast Company)</a>
