    <h3 itemprop="headline">Minnesota lawmakers agree to nuclear energy</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Supporters hope it's the first step toward lifting the state's 32-year-old moratorium on new nuclear plants in the state. They say Minnesota needs nuclear energy to help meet its goal of carbon-free electricity.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/05/26/minnesota-lawmakers-agree-to-study-possibility-of-building-new-nuclear-plants/"  >(Kirsti Marohn, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 26 May 2026 19:29:36 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 26 May 2026 19:29:36 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/05/26/maryland-ballot-blunder-sparks-house-gop-probe-ahead-primary.webp" alt="Maryland ballot blunder sparks House GOP probe ahead of primary" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Maryland ballot blunder sparks House GOP probe ahead of primary</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      GOP lawmakers scrutinized Maryland&apos;s mail-in ballot error that led officials to resend ballots to some voters before the June 23 primary.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/05/26/maryland-ballot-blunder-sparks-house-gop-probe-ahead-primary/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 22 May 2026 20:46:24 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 22 May 2026 20:46:24 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Catharine Richert, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/05/22/rochester-mayoral-race-getting-crowded-as-naacps-elegbede-enters.webp" alt="NAACP&#8217;s Elegbede enters crowded Rochester mayoral race" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">NAACP&#8217;s Elegbede enters crowded Rochester mayoral race</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The field of candidates vying for the top office in the city of Rochester is getting crowded. The latest to enter is the local NAACP president, bringing the number of announced candidates to seven.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/05/22/rochester-mayoral-race-getting-crowded-as-naacps-elegbede-enters/"  >(Catharine Richert, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset></main>
